data.description:
Welcome to the allure of 3019 Tammaway Dr, Midlothian! This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence is situated in a dynamic community, offering a perfect blend of convenience and charm. Immerse yourself in the local scene with an array of shopping and dining options just moments away.

Experience the vibrant pulse of the neighborhood as you explore eclectic eateries and boutique shops. Enjoy the ease of access to parks, creating opportunities for leisurely strolls or outdoor activities. This area exudes a lively atmosphere that caters to various interests.

With a fully fenced in backyard allowing for creative outdoor space utilization. Imagine creating your own oasis or an inviting outdoor lounge area. Enjoy the serene view with a fully screened in porch.

3019 Tammaway Dr invites you to embrace a lifestyle where every day brings new discoveries and the community adds a vibrant backdrop to your experiences. Seize the opportunity to make this residence your own – where convenience, style, and a touch of individuality converge seamlessly. Your next chapter begins here!
